sample code for Lyft apprenticeship application

The app performs the following:

Accept a POST request to the route “/test”, which accepts one argument “string_to_cut”
Return a JSON object with the key “return_string” and a string containing every third letter from the original string
(e.g.) If you POST {"string_to_cut": "iamyourlyftdriver"}, it will return: {"return_string": "muydv"}.

command to test app: curl -X POST https://lyft-interview-test.glitch.me/test --data '{"string_to_cut": "iamyourlyftdriver"}' -H 'Content-Type: application/json'
